---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABand from '@/components/CTABand.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Travel Insurance | Heidi Blondin Financial"
  description="Emergency medical, trip cancellation, and baggage coverage for every trip. Travel insurance arranged through Heidi Blondin Financial and TravelUnderwriters."
>

  <section class="bg-brand-plum py-20">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow-light mb-5">Insurance</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-white text-balance" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Travel Insurance</h1>
      <p class="font-sans text-[18px] text-white/65 mt-5 leading-relaxed">
        A medical emergency outside your province can cost tens of thousands of dollars. Travel insurance covers you when your provincial plan falls short — which is almost everywhere outside Ontario.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-6" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Why OHIP isn't enough</h2>
      <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>Ontario's health insurance covers you for essential services — but outside of Ontario, that coverage drops significantly. Out-of-province emergencies, and especially out-of-country emergencies, can result in hospital bills that OHIP barely covers. In the United States, a single ambulance ride or emergency room visit can run thousands of dollars before treatment begins.</p>
        <p>Travel insurance ensures that a medical emergency doesn't turn into a financial one.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <div class="bg-brand-tintPlum p-6">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">Emergency Medical</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[13px] text-brand-ink/65 leading-relaxed">The core of most travel plans — covers hospitalization, physician fees, prescription drugs, ambulance, and medical evacuation if needed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-tintPlum p-6">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">Trip Cancellation & Interruption</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[13px] text-brand-ink/65 leading-relaxed">Reimburses non-refundable trip costs if you must cancel before departure or cut a trip short due to a covered reason (illness, death in family, etc.).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-tintPlum p-6">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">Baggage & Travel Delay</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[13px] text-brand-ink/65 leading-relaxed">Covers lost, stolen, or damaged baggage and may cover additional expenses from flight delays or missed connections.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-4" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Important for snowbirds and frequent travellers</h2>
        <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-3">
          <p>If you spend extended periods outside Canada — as many Ontario retirees do during winter — you need to ensure your travel insurance covers multi-trip or annual plans, and that your provincial residency status doesn't lapse. Some plans have restrictions for pre-existing conditions or age limits that matter for older travellers.</p>
          <p>We help clients navigate these details before they matter — not after.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 bg-brand-plum p-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-5">
        <div>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">Ready to get coverage for your trip?</p>
          <p class="font-sans text-xs text-white/60">We arrange travel insurance through TravelUnderwriters — click to get a quote directly.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.travelunderwriters.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary-gold flex-shrink-0">Get a Travel Quote</a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 bg-brand-tintPlum p-5 border-l-2 border-brand-plum/30">
        <p class="font-sans text-xs text-brand-ink/55 leading-relaxed">Insurance products are offered through Heidi Blondin Financial / Qualified Financial Services. Travel insurance is subject to policy terms, conditions, and exclusions. Please read your policy carefully before travelling. This article is for general information purposes only and does not constitute personalized insurance advice.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABand heading="Travel with confidence" sub="Book a free consultation and we'll make sure you're covered before your next trip." />

</BaseLayout>
